OL,4,Ctook on role due to no other options `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FCharities and campaigners have been
OL,8,Fcalling on political parties to make
OL,9,Freforming social care a priority, with
OL,10,Funmet need in the system seen to be
OL,11,Fputting pressure on those providing
OL,12,Funpaid care.
OL,14,FSome 62% of carers surveyed, which
OL,15,FCarers UK said is equivalent to 10
OL,16,Fmillion people based on population
OL,17,Fdata, reported having no other option
OL,18,Fbut to become an unpaid carer.
