OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"The shift from hospital to home,
OL,8,Fsmaller families and changing
OL,9,Fdemographics could also be a
OL,10,Fcontributing factor."
OL,12,FWhile the YouGov Omnibus polling found
OL,13,Fthe impact of caring to be more
OL,14,Fnegative than positive across all
OL,15,Faspects asked about, such as jobs,
OL,16,Fpensions and relationships, results
OL,17,Ffound the negative effects to be "more
OL,18,Fpronounced" for those who said they
OL,19,Fhad no choice but to take on a caring
OL,20,Frole.
