OL,7,FCarers UK said it is calling for
OL,8,F"concrete measures from the next
OL,9,Fgovernment to lessen these negative
OL,10,Fimpacts of caring which can be
OL,11,Fdevastating and enduring in carers'
OL,12,Flives".
OL,14,FA legal entitlement to unpaid leave
OL,15,Ffor carers came into effect in April,
OL,16,Fapplying to more than two million
OL,17,Fworkers in England, Wales and Scotland
OL,18,Fwith unpaid caring responsibilities.
