OL,7,FUnder the Carer's Leave Act employees
OL,8,Fwho are carers can take up to a week
OL,9,Fof unpaid leave every 12 months `
OL,10,Fequating to five days for most people.
OL,12,FBut Carers UK chief executive, Helen
OL,13,FWalker, said there is much more to be
OL,14,Fdone to support unpaid carers.
