OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FShe said: "Measures like paid carer's
OL,8,Fleave to prevent employees from
OL,9,Fleaving the labour market early in
OL,10,Forder to care, improvements in carers'
OL,11,Fbenefits to reduce financial hardship,
OL,12,Fsustainable funding for care and
OL,13,Fbreaks to support carers' mental
OL,14,Fhealth and wellbeing as well as new
OL,15,Fduties on the NHS to promote carers'
OL,16,Fhealth and wellbeing.
OL,18,F"Unpaid carers provide a staggering
OL,19,F#162 billion of care a year looking
OL,20,Fafter severely disabled, chronically
OL,21,Fill and older relatives and friends.
