OL,7,F"When so many unpaid carers have no
OL,8,Fchoice about caring, the next
OL,9,FGovernment has a responsibility to
OL,10,Fcare about them, too."
OL,12,FDavid Fothergill, from the Local
OL,13,FGovernment Association, said: "Helping
OL,14,Fcouncils to better support unpaid
OL,15,Fcarers should be a crucial part of a
OL,16,Flong-term and sustainable funding
OL,17,Fsolution for social care.
