OL,7,F"Our Local Government White Paper
OL,8,Fcalls for more support for unpaid
OL,9,Fcarers and a renewed focus on
OL,10,Fprevention and it is crucial that
OL,11,Fwhoever forms the next government
OL,12,Fshould work to support them to
OL,13,Fcontinue their vital role.
OL,15,F"Investing more in early action is
OL,16,Ffundamental to ensuring someone can
OL,17,Fcontinue living independently in the
OL,18,Fhome and community they love."
